>     weight(totalpop1750) summary_measures

Under the common trends assumption,
the TWFE coefficient beta, equal to 0.6339, estimates the sum of several terms.

The first term is a weighted sum of 8 ATTs of the treatment.
7 ATTs receive a positive weight, and 1 receive a negative weight.
